{"word":"ἀνοίγω","slug":"ἀνοίγω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀνοίγω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, οἴγω</el> ‘open’ = the later <el>οἴγνυμι</el>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ tr.\">tr.</a> <b><i>to open</i></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> of doors: <b><a href='B:510 5:19'>Ac 5:19</a>; <a href='B:510 12:10'>12:10</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> <el>ἠνοίγη</el> with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ act.\">act.</a> force, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> 2 below); <b><a href='B:730 4:1'>Rv 4:1</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ abs.\">abs.</a> <b><a href='B:510 5:23'>Ac 5:23</a>;</b> also in imagery <b>14:27; <a href='B:540 2:12'>2 Cor 2:12</a>; <a href='B:580 4:3'>Col 4:3</a>; <a href='B:730 3:8'>Rv 3:8</a>, <a href='B:730 3:20'>20</a>.</b> Other objects <b><a href='B:470 2:11'>Mt 2:11</a>; <a href='B:470 17:27'>17:27</a>; <a href='B:470 27:52'>27:52</a>; <a href='B:490 4:17'>Lk 4:17</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a>; <a href='B:510 9:8'>Ac 9:8</a>; <a href='B:520 3:13'>Ro 3:13</a>; <a href='B:730 5:9'>Rv 5:9</a>; <a href='B:730 9:2'>9:2</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ esp.\">esp.</a> eyes with focus on restoration of sight <b><a href='B:470 9:30'>Mt 9:30</a>; <a href='B:500 9:10'>J 9:10</a>; <a href='B:500 10:21'>10:21</a>; <a href='B:510 26:18'>Ac 26:18</a></b> (in imagery); ears restored to health <b><a href='B:480 7:35'>Mk 7:35</a>.</b> Idiom: <el>ἀ. <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:στόμα\">στόμα</a></el> <i>begin to speak</i> <b><a href='B:470 5:2'>Mt 5:2</a>; <a href='B:470 13:35'>13:35</a>; <a href='B:510 8:35'>Ac 8:35</a>; <a href='B:510 18:14'>18:14</a>; <a href='B:730 13:6'>Rv 13:6</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ intr.\">intr.</a>, in 2 <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pf.\">pf.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνέῳγα\">ἀνέῳγα</a></el> <b><i>to be open</i></b> heaven <b><a href='B:500 1:51'>J 1:51</a>;</b> mouth, <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:στόμα\">στόμα</a> ἡμῶν ἀνέῳγεν</el> in sense of ‘speak freely’<b> <a href='B:540 6:11'>2 Cor 6:11</a>;</b> door, in imagery <b><a href='B:530 16:9'>1 Cor 16:9</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἄνοια\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνοικοδομέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}